column2: select b.ra as lam_ra, b.dec as lam_dec, a.ra as SDSS_ra, a.dec as SDSS_dec, a.petroMag_u, a.petroMag_g , a.petroMag_r , a.petroMag_i , a.petroMag_z into mydb.cross_petroMag from mydb.cross_mag as b. CROSS APPLY dbo.fGetNearestObjEq (b.ra, b.dec, #) as c join DR1#.PhotoObjAll as a on a.objid = b.objid.
